<DocsLayout
  title="Install hitlimit-bun - Bun Native Rate Limiter | Memory-first Performance"
  description="Install hitlimit-bun for Bun applications. Memory-first design achieving 6M+ ops/sec with native bun:sqlite and Redis support. The fastest rate limiter for Bun.serve, Hono, and Elysia."
  keywords="bun install hitlimit, bun rate limiter, hitlimit-bun install, bun add rate limit, elysia rate limit, bun:sqlite rate limit, bun native package"
>
  <h1>Bun Installation</h1>

  <p>Install hitlimit for Bun using the Bun package manager.</p>

  <h2 id="install">Install the Package</h2>

  <Tabs
    tabs={[
      { label: 'bun', content: 'bun add @joint-ops/hitlimit-bun' },
    ]}
  />

  <p>
    The <code>hitlimit-bun</code> package is optimized specifically for Bun and includes
    native SQLite store support out of the box.
  </p>

  <h2 id="verify">Verify Installation</h2>

  <p>Create a test file to verify the installation:</p>

  <div class="code-block">
    <div class="code-header">
      <div class="code-dots">
        <span class="dot red"></span>
        <span class="dot yellow"></span>
        <span class="dot green"></span>
      </div>
      <span class="code-filename">test.ts</span>
    </div>
    <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span> {"{"} hitlimit {"}"} <span class="kw">from</span> <span class="str">'@joint-ops/hitlimit-bun'</span>

<span class="kw">const</span> limiter = <span class="fn">hitlimit</span>({"{"} limit: <span class="num">10</span>, window: <span class="str">'1m'</span> {"}"})

console.<span class="fn">log</span>(<span class="str">'hitlimit-bun installed successfully!'</span>)</code></pre>
  </div>

  <p>Run the test:</p>

  <Tabs tabs={[{ label: 'bun', content: 'bun run test.ts' }]} />

  <h2 id="optional-deps">Optional Dependencies</h2>

  <p>For Redis support in Bun, install the <code>ioredis</code> peer dependency:</p>

  <Tabs tabs={[{ label: 'bun', content: 'bun add ioredis' }]} />

  <h2 id="requirements">Requirements</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Bun</strong>: v1.0.0 or higher</li>
    <li><strong>TypeScript</strong>: v5.0 or higher (optional but recommended)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="next-steps">Next Steps</h2>

  <p>Now that you have hitlimit-bun installed, proceed to the <a href="/docs/bun/quick-start">Quick Start</a> guide.</p>
</DocsLayout>

